<div class="nlay-intro">
	<div class="inside">
		<div class="text">
			<h1>Woof Gang Bakery</h1>
			<h2>Woof Gang Bakery is the leading specialty retailer of pet food, pet supplies and professional pet grooming in North America,<span> with more than 110 locations across the U.S.</span></h2>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="nlay-boxes tan">
	<div class="text">
		<p>Woof Gang Bakery offers the very best in pet care by providing quality products and grooming with a service-oriented approach. Each location is a neighborhood store committed to the well-being, health and happiness of pets.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="images">
		<%=image_tag('sign.jpg', class: 'img-responsive img1', alt: '') %>
		<%=image_tag('puff-nlay.jpg', class: 'img-responsive img2', alt: '') %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="nlay-intro franch">
	<div class="inside">
		<div class="text">
			<h4>Our approach to franchising is very simple:</h4>
			<p class="two">Successful franchising is built upon successful franchisees.<br> Our leadership philosophy is based upon the belief that we should direct, not dominate the franchise system, and that our franchisees should have a voice and participate in that direction.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="banner-locations">
	<div class="inside med2">
		<h4>More Than 110 Locations Nationwide</h4>
		<div class="btn-hlf">
			<%= link_to "Find One Near You", locations_path, class: 'woof-link' %>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


<div class="nlay-service">
	<div class="logo-row top">
		<div class="inside">
			<%= link_to retail_path, class: 'serve-tl' do %>
	      <%= image_tag('wg-logo1.png', class: 'navbar-item logo')%>
			<% end %>

			<%= link_to grooming_path, class: 'serve-tl' do %>
	      <%= image_tag('wgb-groom.png', class: 'navbar-item logo')%>
			<% end %>

			<%= link_to vet_clinic_path, class: 'serve-tl vet' do %>
	      <%= image_tag('wgb-wellness.png', class: 'navbar-item logo')%>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="full mid tan">
		<div class="inside">
      <div class="image"><%= image_tag('retail7.jpg', class: 'img-responsive')%></div>

			<div class="text">
				<h3>Woof Gang Bakery does it all</h3>
				<!-- <p class="top">We offer a number of services to help keep your pets healthy and spoiled!</p> -->
				<p>We offer a number of services to help keep your pets healthy and spoiled!<br>
				 	Contact your local Woof Gang Bakery to find out which services are available in your area.<br>
					Select a service from the logos displayed to visit the page, and learn more.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="logo-row btm">
		<div class="inside">
			<%= link_to doggie_daycare_path, class: 'serve-tl long daycare' do %>
	      <%= image_tag('wgb-daycare.png', class: 'navbar-item logo')%>
			<% end %>

			<%= link_to doggie_daycare_path, class: 'serve-tl long' do %>
	      <%= image_tag('wgb-daycare.png', class: 'navbar-item logo')%>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

